-- guardian_player_only.lua
-- Plethora/Neural Interface guardian.
--
-- Changes from old version:
--   - Admin/player whitelist is all at the top.
--   - Laser power/range/delay are adjustable up top.
--   - Tries to shoot ONLY non-whitelisted players, not mobs/items.
--   - Prints nearby non-whitelisted entities it sees, with TARGET / ignored reason.
--   - Uses pcall around sense/fire/walk so one bad entity does not crash the program.

-- =========================================================
-- === CONFIGURATION
-- =========================================================

